
This is a simple and interactive Quiz Application developed using React.js. It allows users to attempt multiple-choice questions, get instant feedback on their answers, and view their final score at the end of the quiz.

## 🚀 Features

- ✅ Multiple-choice questions
- ✅ Answer validation (correct/wrong highlighting)
- ✅ Score tracking
- ✅ Next question navigation
- ✅ Final result screen
- ✅ Restart quiz option
- ✅ Clean and responsive UI

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- React.js
- JavaScript (ES6)
- CSS

## 📚 Concepts Used

- React Functional Components
- useState Hook
- Event Handling
- Conditional Rendering
- Dynamic UI updates

## ▶️ How to Run

```bash
npm install
npm run dev
